  "title": "Fish Smoker - Stardew Valley Wiki",
  "description": "The Fish Smoker is a type of Artisan Equipment that is used to create smoked fish using any fish and 1 coal. It doubles the sell price of a fish while retaining quality, as well as multiplying the energy and health restoration by 1.5 (if that fish restored energy or health, otherwise the value remains unchanged).[1] The smoker accepts Legendary Fish as well as Crab Pot specific fish, making the latter edible.[2]",
